OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfcom urged to toughen TV  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frules for MP presenters    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The media expert who drew up the UK's  
OL,6, broadcasting rules has urged the       
OL,7, watchdog, Ofcom, to decide whether     
OL,8, politicians should be allowed to       
OL,9, present TV programmes on news channels.
OL,11,FChris Banatvala said no-one foresaw the
OL,12,Frise of politician presenters when the 
OL,13,Frules were being designed in the 2000s.
OL,15,FHe said Ofcom should take "a view about
OL,16,Fwhether what is emerging is acceptable 
OL,17,Fin terms of due impartiality".         
OL,19,FThe regulator is reviewing its rules   
OL,20,Faround politicians presenting TV shows.
